high_descs: Turn to the right, go forward, hang a left and go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn around and go to the microwave that is on the left.
Put the knife inside the microwave.
Turn to the left, go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around and go to the microwave that is on the left.
Put the tomato in the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the tomato when it is done cooking.
Turn to the left to face the sink.
Put the tomato on the counter in front of the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked tomato on a counter.

high_descs: Go to the right of the sink
Grab the large knife off of the counter
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices
Turn around and go to the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Turn left and stop at the sink
Grab a slice of tomato off of the counter
Turn around and go to the microwave
Heat the tomato in the microwave and then take it out
Turn to the left and face the sink
Put the tomato on the counter in the front of the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot tomato slice in front of the sink

high_descs: Locate the microwave on your right.
Pick up a knife from the counter.
Cut the tomato at the right corner of the counter into slices.
Turn around and go to the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave door, put the knife in the microwave and close the door.
Turn left and go to the counter.
Pick up one slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Open the  microwave door and put the tomato slice in the microwave. Close the door and cook for 5 minutes. Open the microwave door and take out the tomato slice.
Turn left and go to the counter.
Put the tomato slice on the edge of the counter near the bigger sink.
anns.task_desc: Cook a tomato slice in a microwave and put it on the edge of a counter near a bigger sink.
